metadata.author: Jeff Kinney
metadata.description: Greg Heffley has always been in a hurry to grow up.But is getting older really all it's cracked up to be?Greg suddenly finds himself dealing with the pressures of boy-girl parties, increased responsibilities, and even the awkward changes that come with getting older - all without his best friend, Rowley, at his side.Can Greg make it through on his own? Or will he have to face the 'ugly truth'?
